{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":62048,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":10617,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你可以谴责，我为什么不可以支持","timestamp":1593409593,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62049,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":10617,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"随便谴责 也随便被谴责","timestamp":1593409603,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62062,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":10617,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我为什么就不能讨论？","timestamp":1593409719,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62066,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":10617,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你谴责你的，我讨论我的。","timestamp":1593409759,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62077,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":10617,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你以为你是中美吗？谴责就谴责呗，你还可以密切关注","timestamp":1593409865,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62220,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":10617,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"法律是底线，在这个底线之上是不违法的，但不是不能谴责的。","timestamp":1593411176,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":63111,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":10617,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"同学，你可以稍微了解一下法律。法律并不仅仅只有行政法和刑法，中国大部分法律纠纷都是民法案件。在民法中成文法是要求大家讲市场道德的。你可以看看我国民法典一开始的几条都是在讲原则。比如说，要遵守绿色原则。法律其实有更多价值关怀，如果违反了法律所倡导的价值，即使没有违反具体的禁止性条文，我觉得应该也是有可谴责性的。","timestamp":1593421880,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":10617,"reply":7,"tag":null,"text":"是不是只要法律不禁止，我们就不能谴责？为什么？","timestamp":1593409501,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782588,"url":"","vote":{}}}